    {
      "type": "action",
      "name": "Parasocial Leech",
      "system": {
        "actionType": {
          "value": "action"
        },
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The dredgelit leeches vitality from a creature in their fan club. The dredgelit attempts a Performance check against the Will DC of the creature. The creature takes @Damage[6d6[void]] damage, and the dredgelit regains @Damage[10[healing]] Hit Points.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target takes double damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned 2} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.eIcWbB5o3pP6OIMe]{Immobilized} for 1 round.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes full damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.dfCMdR4wnpbYNTix]{Stunned 1} and immobilized for 1 round.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is unaffected. The dredgelit's abysmal performance results in them taking @Damage[2d8[mental]] damage instead of regaining Hit Points.</p>",
          "gm": ""
        },
